channel.title: Problem logging in
channel.description: Hello i just got my first online server up yesterday and left it running through the night (a mistake i know) so when i got up i saw it was closed out i figured my dad closed it well apperantly thats not the case i tried to bring back up my run.bat and it said error port 43594 already in use... so i somhow i fixed that now it says its online agian but when i try to log on with my server ip it says error connecting to sever so i tried with 127.0.0.1 and what do you know that still works is there anyway to get it online agian? prefferably soon? and i checked the chat logs and stuff no one tried to crash it[br][br][size=1]Posted on: December 03, 2009, 12:33:10 pm[/size][hr]NEVERMIND it works agian sorry for wasting your time
